<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 12:25:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>瑞典电动汽车制造商 Polestar 开始在美国生产，避免高额关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/swedish-ev-maker-polestar-starts-us-production-avoiding-heavy-tariffs-2024-08-14/</link><description>周三，瑞典电动汽车 (EV) 制造商 Polestar 在避免对中国制造的汽车征收高额关税方面又迈出了一步，该汽车制造商表示已开始在美国生产 Polestar 3 SUV。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 12:03:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/swedish-ev-maker-polestar-starts-us-production-avoiding-heavy-tariffs-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国海军最新空对空导弹可能会打破南海平衡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-navys-newest-air-to-air-missile-could-tilt-balance-south-china-sea-2024-08-14/</link><description>专家表示，美国海军在印太地区部署新型超远程空对空导弹可能会消除中国在空中射程方面的优势，这是在该地区紧张局势下加强力量投送的一部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 11:10:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-navys-newest-air-to-air-missile-could-tilt-balance-south-china-sea-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国重新提交在伦敦设立有争议的大型大使馆的申请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-resubmits-application-build-contested-big-embassy-london-2024-08-14/</link><description>中国重新提交了在伦敦建造一座新的大型大使馆的计划，这是一个有争议的项目，可能会考验新工党政府在经历多年的外交紧张和争端后如何处理与世界第二大经济体的关系。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 11:07:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-resubmits-application-build-contested-big-embassy-london-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>中方敦促美英澳不要推进核潜艇合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-us-uk-australia-not-advance-nuclear-submarine-cooperation-2024-08-14/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，在国际社会就保障监督等问题达成共识之前，美国、英国和澳大利亚不应推进核潜艇合作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 11:04:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-us-uk-australia-not-advance-nuclear-submarine-cooperation-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国清理通胀，新西兰意外降息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-14/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 10:07:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>香港活动人士因监狱投诉表格案被判入狱三天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-activist-gets-three-days-jail-prison-complaint-form-case-2024-08-14/</link><description>周三，香港一家法院将民主活动人士周欧文 (Owen Chow) 监禁三天，并对其律师胡菲丽斯 (Phyllis Woo) 处以罚款，原因是他未经授权将一份文件带出监狱。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 09:21:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-activist-gets-three-days-jail-prison-complaint-form-case-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>游戏业务复苏，腾讯第二季度收入增长8%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tencents-q2-revenue-up-8-recovery-game-business-2024-08-14/</link><description>中国腾讯控股周三公布第二季度收入增长 8%，主要得益于 5 月份推出的新手机游戏开局强劲，游戏业务复苏。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 08:44:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tencents-q2-revenue-up-8-recovery-game-business-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国最新的大片对零工经济进行了罕见的严厉审视</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-blockbuster-casts-rare-harsh-light-gig-economy-2024-08-14/</link><description>今年夏天在中国影院上映的最大电影之一解决了中国最大的几个经济痛点：不确定的就业市场、向下流动以及数百万人打零工的艰苦生活。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 08:11:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-blockbuster-casts-rare-harsh-light-gig-economy-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国啤酒前景黯淡，嘉士伯股价触及29个月新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/carlsberg-ceo-sees-weak-chinese-beer-market-also-h2-2024-08-14/</link><description>嘉士伯对中国市场的前景感到悲观，因为中国啤酒消费者越来越多地选择放弃最昂贵的品牌，导致其股价跌至 2022 年 3 月以来的最低水平。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 07:39:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/carlsberg-ceo-sees-weak-chinese-beer-market-also-h2-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国利率前景和出口强劲，亚洲债券吸引大量资金流入</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/asian-bonds-attract-hefty-inflows-us-rate-outlook-strong-exports-2024-08-14/</link><description>受地区出口强劲增长以及美联储 9 月降息预期的刺激，外国投资者 7 月连续第三个月成为亚洲债券的净买家。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 07:38:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/asian-bonds-attract-hefty-inflows-us-rate-outlook-strong-exports-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>经济出现新的疲软迹象，中国官员没有喘息的机会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/no-respite-chinese-officials-economy-shows-new-signs-weakness-2024-08-14/</link><description>最近一系列惨淡的指标降低了人们对 7 月份中国经济表现的预期，这对 2024 年剩余时间来说是一个不祥的迹象，并表明除了缓解世界第二大经济体的痛点之外，还需要采取更多刺激措施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 07:09:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/no-respite-chinese-officials-economy-shows-new-signs-weakness-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国调查殡仪馆和服务机构中猖獗的腐败行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-probes-rampant-graft-funeral-homes-services-2024-08-14/</link><description>官方媒体周三称，中国揭露了殡葬服务行业普遍存在的腐败现象，殡仪馆的长期管理人员和官员犯下非法收费和乱建墓地等违法行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 05:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-probes-rampant-graft-funeral-homes-services-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>新加坡丰益国际 (Wilmar) 因食品部门实力强劲而实现高收益利润，阿达尼丰益 (Adani Wilmar) 盈利增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/singapores-wilmar-posts-higher-hy-profit-food-unit-strength-higher-adani-wilmar-2024-08-14/</link><description>新加坡农业企业丰益国际 (Wilmar International) 上半年利润小幅上涨，反映出其食品业务表现较好，并得益于阿达尼丰益 (Adani Wilmar) 合资企业盈利的增加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 04:47:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/singapores-wilmar-posts-higher-hy-profit-food-unit-strength-higher-adani-wilmar-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>早上竞价：欢迎来到切割俱乐部，新西兰人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-14/</link><description>Stella Qiu 展望欧洲和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 04:33:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>日本首相岸田下台的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/reactions-japans-pm-kishida-stepping-down-2024-08-14/</link><description>日本首相岸田文雄表示，他将于九月下台，结束因政治丑闻而受损的三年任期，并为新首相应对物价上涨的影响铺平道路。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 04:02:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/reactions-japans-pm-kishida-stepping-down-2024-08-14/</guid></item></channel></rss>